### Identity Service – HTTP test file
### Use with JetBrains HTTP Client or VS Code REST Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### ── REGISTER ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### ── LOGIN ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### ── REFRESH TOKEN ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "<paste_refresh_token_here>"
}

### ── LOGOUT ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/auth/logout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "<paste_refresh_token_here>"
}

### ── VALIDATE TOKEN (used by BFF) ───────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/auth/validate?token=<paste_access_token_here>

### ── GET MY PROFILE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <paste_access_token_here>

### ── CHANGE PASSWORD ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

PUT {{baseUrl}}/identity/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer <paste_access_token_here>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "currentPassword": "Password123",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword456"
}

### ── HEALTH CHECK ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ── SWAGGER UI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger
